      • random

        public static int random(int start,
                         int end)
        a method that will produce a number based on the start number and end number
        参数:
        start - the start number
        end - the end number
        返回:
        any number in between the start and the end

      • getIntFromColor

        public static int getIntFromColor(int Red,
                                  int Green,
                                  int Blue)
        a method that will change rgb value to an int
        参数:
        Red - the red value of a color
        Green - the green value of a color
        Blue - the blue value of a color
        返回:
        integer that is converted based on the color

      • toBufferedImage

        public static java.awt.image.BufferedImage toBufferedImage(java.awt.Image img)
        a method that will change an image to a buffered image
        参数:
        img - the Image needed to be changed
        返回:
        the same image but to a buffered image type

      • findAvg

        public static float findAvg(java.util.TreeMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.Float> temp,
                            java.lang.String specificDate)
        find the average based on the arrayList and the key date
        参数:
        temp - the treeMap of temperatures
        specificDate - the String of a specific Date
        返回:
        //return the average of that selected date

      • makeTransparent

        public static java.awt.AlphaComposite makeTransparent(float alpha)
        the method that will return a composite based on the float value passed it, it is used to set the transparency of the component drawn
        参数:
        alpha - the transparency of the graphics (1 to be opaque, 0 to be transparent)
        返回:
        return the AlphaComposite that can be used to change the transparency of the graphics
